Package com.github.webapp_minifier

The Webapp Minifier plugin minifies CSS and JavaScript either embedded in or reference by HTML files.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultTagHandler
    This class provides the default NodeHandler implementation.
    HelpMojo
    Display help information on webapp-minifier-maven-plugin.
    Call mvn webapp-minifier:help -Ddetail=true -Dgoal=<goal-name> to display parameter details.
    MinificationContext
    This class defines the context for a minification session.
    MinifiedFileBuilder
    This class assists in the creation of MinifiedFileInfo instances.
    MinifiedFileInfo
    This class contains details about a minified file.
    WebappMinifierMojo
    Minifies the web application.
    WebappMinifierReportMojo
    Generates a report summarizing the minification performed on the web application.

Package com.github.webapp_minifier Description
